* 设置文字无法被选中 */        }      </style>      <!-- The content below will be included at the end of the <head> element. --><script type="text/javascript">  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {    // your code here  });</script></head><body for="html-export">              <div class="crossnote markdown-preview  ">      <div class="md-toc"><div class="md-toc-link-wrapper" style="padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:18px">          <a href="#一-准备工作" class="md-toc-link">            <p>一、准备工作</p>          </a></div><div class="md-toc-link-wrapper" style="padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:18px">          <a href="#二-模板讲解" class="md-toc-link">            <p>二、模板讲解</p>          </a></div><div class="md-toc-link-wrapper" style="padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:18px">          <a href="#三-图片的插入" class="md-toc-link">            <p>三、图片的插入</p>          </a></div><div class="md-toc-link-wrapper" style="padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:18px">          <a href="#latexyufa" class="md-toc-link">            <p>附录一、LaTeX基本语法</p>          </a></div><div class="md-toc-link-wrapper" style="padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:18px">          <a href="#shuxuehuanjing" class="md-toc-link">            <p>附录二、模板自带的数学环境</p>          </a></div></div><h1 id="一-准备工作">一、准备工作 </h1><ol><li>解压模板压缩包</li><li>安装CTeX套装</li><li>显示文件扩展名</li><li>将输入法设置为 "中文状态下使用英文标点" (如果需要使用中文标点, 切换回原来的输入法即可)</li></ol><h1 id="二-模板讲解">二、模板讲解 </h1><ol><li><p>初识模板</p></li><li><p>摘要abstract</p></li><li><p>正文body</p><ol><li><a href="#latexyufa">LaTeX基本语法</a></li><li>WinEdt的符号面板<br><strong>温馨提示</strong>: 如果大家发现自己的WinEdt界面缺少了某一部分功能, 基本上都能在第一排的<code>View</code>处找到.</li><li>WinEdt的自动补全<br>输入<code>\begin&#123;xxx&#125;&#125;</code>自动补全为<code>\begin&#123;xxx&#125;...\end&#123;xxx&#125;</code></li><li>simpletex将公式图片转化为LaTeX代码 <a href="https://www.simpletex.cn/ai/latex_ocr" target="_blank">https://www.simpletex.cn/ai/latex_ocr</a> (类似的网站还有<a href="https://www.latexlive.com" target="_blank">https://www.latexlive.com</a> 等)</li><li>百度或者AI辅助编程, 比如 <a href="https://chatglm.cn" target="_blank">https://chatglm.cn</a> 与 <a href="https://kimi.moonshot.cn" target="_blank">https://kimi.moonshot.cn</a> 等. 大家可以向AI提出自己的需求, 然后由AI帮忙生成代码, 也可以将一段看不懂或者报错的代码交给AI分析, 从而了解相应的语法、改正错误.</li><li><a href="#shuxuehuanjing">模板自带的一些数学环境</a><br>定义、定理、引理、命题、证明、推论、性质、注、例、分析、解、练习</li></ol><p><strong>注意</strong>: 为了便于排查错误, 建议大家在进行正文写作的时候尽量写一部分就回到myTemlplate.tex中编译一次.</p></li><li><p>参考文献bibfile</p><pre data-role="codeBlock" data-info="latex" class="language-latex latex"><code><span class="token function selector">\bibitem</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>lz<span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>   李忠.   <span class="token function selector">\textsl</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>并不神秘的非欧几何<span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span>M<span class="token punctuation">]</span>. 北京: 高等教育出版社, 2010.</code></pre><p><strong>温馨提示</strong>:<br>(1) <code>\bibitem</code>的参数不要有中文和空格. 例如<code>\bibitem&#123;lz abc&#125;</code>和<code>\bibitem&#123;李忠&#125;</code>是不被允许的.<br>(2) 若引用参考文献之后生成的PDF出现<code>[?]</code>, 只需再次编译即可.</p></li><li><p>致谢thanks</p></li><li><p>附录fulu</p></li><li><p>声明shengming</p></li></ol><h1 id="三-图片的插入">三、图片的插入 </h1><p><strong>步骤</strong>:</p><ol><li>将图片文件放到模板内的<code>myfigure</code>文件夹中.</li><li>在body.tex中相应位置插入如下代码:</li></ol><pre data-role="codeBlock" data-info="latex" class="language-latex latex"><code><span class="token function selector">\begin</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-figure">figure</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span>htbp<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token function selector">\centering</span><span class="token function selector">\includegraphics</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span>width=6cm<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>图片文件名<span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="token function selector">\caption</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>图片标题<span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="token function selector">\end</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-figure">figure</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span></code></pre><ol start="3"><li>保存body.tex, 回到myTemplate.tex编译即可.</li></ol><p><strong>温馨提示</strong>:<br>(1) 图片文件名不要有中文和空格, 例如<code>图片1.png</code>、<code>abc def.jpg</code>等是不允许的, 会出现报错.<br>(2) LaTeX会根据页面留白自动调整图片的位置, 因此pdf中图片的实际位置可能与图片代码所处的位置不一致, 这是正常的.<br>(3) 论文中不要出现 "如下图所示" 等语句, 而应该使用 "如图x所示".<br>(4) 除了png、jpg等常见的位图之外, LaTeX还支持插入pdf等矢量图.<br>(5) LaTeX自身也能作图 <a href="https://www.mathcha.io/editor" target="_blank">https://www.mathcha.io/editor</a></p><h1 id="latexyufa">附录一、LaTeX基本语法 </h1><ol><li>标题<br>一级标题<code>\section&#123;...&#125;</code><br>二级标题<code>\subsection&#123;...&#125;</code><br>三级标题<code>\subsubsection&#123;...&#125;</code></li><li>分段<br>LaTeX使用空行表示分段, 即两个不同的段落之间需要留一个空行.</li><li>数学公式<br>行内公式<code>$...$</code><br>行间公式<code>$$...$$</code>或<code>\[...\]</code><br>带编号的行间公式<code>\begin&#123;equation&#125;...\end&#123;equation&#125;</code></li><li>注释<br>LaTeX将百分号<code>%</code>后的内容视为注释 (即这些内容不会被电脑编译)</li></ol><p>示例:</p><pre data-role="codeBlock" data-info="latex" class="language-latex latex"><code><span class="token function selector">\section</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token headline class-name">一级标题</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>这是第一段的内容. 这是第一段的内容. 这是第一段的内容. 这是第一段的内容. 这是第一段的内容. 这是第一段的内容. 这是第一段的内容. 这是第一段的内容. 这是第一段的内容. 这是第一段的内容. 这是第二段的内容. 这是第二段的内容. 这是第二段的内容. 这是第二段的内容. 这是第二段的内容. 这是第二段的内容. 这是第二段的内容. 这是第二段的内容. 这是第二段的内容. <span class="token function selector">\subsection</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token headline class-name">二级标题</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>欧拉公式<span class="token equation string">$$e^&#123;i<span class="token equation-command regex">\pi</span>&#125;+1=0$$</span>是一个特别美的公式, 其中<span class="token equation string">$i$</span>是虚数单位. 实际上, 它是<span class="token function selector">\begin</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-equation">equation</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="token equation string">  e^&#123;ix&#125;=<span class="token equation-command regex">\cos</span> x+i<span class="token equation-command regex">\sin</span> x</span><span class="token function selector">\end</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-equation">equation</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>的特殊情况. 除了欧拉公式以外, 还有很多公式都是非常漂亮的, 这里我们不再赘述. <span class="token function selector">\subsubsection</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token headline class-name">三级标题</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="token comment">% 这是注释</span>啦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦. <span class="token function selector">\begin</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-definition">definition</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span>莫比乌斯变换<span class="token punctuation">]</span>我们把形如<span class="token equation string">$$T(z)=<span class="token equation-command regex">\frac</span>&#123;az+b&#125;&#123;cz+d&#125;$$</span>的映射<span class="token equation string">$T:<span class="token equation-command regex">\overline</span>&#123;<span class="token equation-command regex">\mathbb</span> C&#125;<span class="token equation-command regex">\to</span><span class="token equation-command regex">\overline</span>&#123;<span class="token equation-command regex">\mathbb</span> C&#125;$</span>称为莫比乌斯变换, 其中<span class="token equation string">$a,b,c,d<span class="token equation-command regex">\in</span><span class="token equation-command regex">\mathbb</span> C$</span>且<span class="token equation string">$ad-bc<span class="token equation-command regex">\ne</span> 0$</span>.<span class="token function selector">\end</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-definition">definition</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span></code></pre><center> <p><img src="https://s21.ax1x.com/2024/07/28/pkqb0oQ.jpg" alt="pkqb0oQ.jpg"></p></center><h1 id="shuxuehuanjing">附录二、模板自带的数学环境 </h1><h3 id="定义">定义 </h3><pre data-role="codeBlock" data-info="latex" class="language-latex latex"><code><span class="token function selector">\begin</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-definition">definition</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>这是定义. <span class="token function selector">\end</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-definition">definition</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span></code></pre><h3 id="定理">定理 </h3><pre data-role="codeBlock" data-info="latex" class="language-latex latex"><code><span class="token function selector">\begin</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-theorem">theorem</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>这是定理. <span class="token function selector">\end</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-theorem">theorem</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span></code></pre><h3 id="引理">引理 </h3><pre data-role="codeBlock" data-info="latex" class="language-latex latex"><code><span class="token function selector">\begin</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-lemma">lemma</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>这是引理. <span class="token function selector">\end</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-lemma">lemma</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span></code></pre><h3 id="命题">命题 </h3><pre data-role="codeBlock" data-info="latex" class="language-latex latex"><code><span class="token function selector">\begin</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-proposition">proposition</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>这是命题. <span class="token function selector">\end</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-proposition">proposition</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span></code></pre><h3 id="证明">证明 </h3><pre data-role="codeBlock" data-info="latex" class="language-latex latex"><code><span class="token function selector">\begin</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-proof">proof</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>这是证明. <span class="token function selector">\end</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-proof">proof</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span></code></pre><h3 id="推论">推论 </h3><pre data-role="codeBlock" data-info="latex" class="language-latex latex"><code><span class="token function selector">\begin</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-corollary">corollary</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>这是推论. <span class="token function selector">\end</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-corollary">corollary</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span></code></pre><h3 id="性质">性质 </h3><pre data-role="codeBlock" data-info="latex" class="language-latex latex"><code><span class="token function selector">\begin</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-property">property</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>这是性质. <span class="token function selector">\end</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-property">property</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span></code></pre><h3 id="注">注 </h3><pre data-role="codeBlock" data-info="latex" class="language-latex latex"><code><span class="token function selector">\begin</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-remark">remark</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>这是注记. <span class="token function selector">\end</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-remark">remark</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span></code></pre><h3 id="例">例 </h3><pre data-role="codeBlock" data-info="latex" class="language-latex latex"><code><span class="token function selector">\begin</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-example">example</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>这是例子. <span class="token function selector">\end</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-example">example</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span></code></pre><h3 id="分析">分析 </h3><pre data-role="codeBlock" data-info="latex" class="language-latex latex"><code><span class="token function selector">\begin</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-analysis">analysis</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>这是分析. <span class="token function selector">\end</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-analysis">analysis</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span></code></pre><h3 id="解">解 </h3><pre data-role="codeBlock" data-info="latex" class="language-latex latex"><code><span class="token function selector">\begin</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-solution">solution</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>这是解答.<span class="token function selector">\end</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-solution">solution</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span></code></pre><h3 id="练习">练习 </h3><pre data-role="codeBlock" data-info="latex" class="language-latex latex"><code><span class="token function selector">\begin</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-exercise">exercise</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>这是练习. <span class="token function selector">\end</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token keyword keyword-exercise">exercise</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span></code></pre>      </div>                  <center class="kaishu unselectable" title="世界上有两种最耀眼的光芒，一种是太阳，一种是数学人努力的模样~" style="font-size: 26px;">        <font color=BD10E0 class="rotate">❀</font><font color=BD10E0 class="rotate">❀</font><font color=BD10E0 class="rotate">❀</font>        祝学弟学妹们前程似锦, 祝数统院越来越好!        <font color=BD10E0 class="rotate">❀</font><font color=BD10E0  class="rotate">❀</font><font color=BD10E0  class="rotate">❀</font>      </center>      <br>      <br>      <br>                           </body></html>]]></content>
      
      
      
